casebody.data:
Abraham B. Wetmore, as executor, &c., respondent, v. Thomas E. Porter, appellant. Decided December 1, 1884. Exceptions heard at general term. Edward Pitch, for appellant. E. Terry, for respondent.

Before Sedgwick, Ch. J. and Van Vorst, J.

Opinion by Van Vorst, J. Judgment affirmed, with costs (see 92 N. Y. 76).
